hardt U "Thrombolytics: drug interactions of clinical significance." Drug Saf 23 (2000):  391-9[8] Hirsch J, Dalen J, Guyatt G, American College of Chest Physicians "The sixth (2000) ACCP guidelines for antithrombotic therapy for prevention and treatment of thrombosis. American College of Physicians." Chest 119(1 Suppl) (2001):  1S-2S', 1767369485);
