ared with acetaminophen." Ann Intern Med 107 (1987):  628-35[2] "Product Information. Toradol (ketorolac)." Roche Laboratories  (2002):[3] "Multum Information Services, Inc. Expert Review Panel"[4] "Product Information. Celebrex (celecoxib)." Searle  (2001):', 1767369485);
